title: Bobby Spends Weekend With Girlfriend’s Parents + Secret Ballot On Eddie Being Allowed Back In Studio + “Don’t Take the Girl” Lyric Debate
itunes:title: Bobby Spends Weekend With Girlfriend’s Parents + Secret Ballot On Eddie Being Allowed Back In Studio + “Don’t Take the Girl” Lyric Debate
description:
Bobby talks about spending the weekend with his girlfriend's parents in Nashville. He said it’s still weird at times because he doesn’t know what to call her Dad. We get another coronavirus update from Eddie who has been positive for 46 days now. Will he be allowed back in studio? Plus, we have a caller with a very interesting question about the end of the song “Don’t Take the Girl” by Tim McGraw!
